title: Borderless Capital Leads Wormhole-Powered $50M Cross-Chain Fund - CoinDesk
content: The fund will be powered by Wormhole, a decentralized message-passing protocol that connects blockchains, enabling them to communicate with each other. The portfolio companies invested by the fund will thus be able to closely collaborate and work with Wormhole as their cross-chain solution, according to Borderless Capital.

title: Hummingbird Spotted In Solana Beach: Photo Of The Day - Patch
content:
SOLANA BEACH, CA — Patch reader Teresa Schaefer captured this photo of an Anna's hummingbird at Annie's Canyon Trail in Solana Beach.

If you have an awesome picture of nature, breathtaking scenery, kids caught being kids, a pet doing something funny or something unusual you happen to catch with your camera, we'd love to feature it on Patch.

We're looking for high-resolution, horizontal images that reflect the beauty that is San Diego County, and that show off your unique talents.

Send your photos to kristina.houck@patch.com. Be sure to include photo credit information, when and where the shot was taken, and any other details about what was going on.
